                                ‚Ä¢ <strong>Bet Calculation:</strong> First + Last numbers = Next Bet<br>
                                ‚Ä¢ <strong>Win:</strong> Remove first and last numbers<br>
                                ‚Ä¢ <strong>Lose:</strong> Add bet amount to end of sequence<br>
                                ‚Ä¢ <strong>Complete:</strong> Sequence empty = Target achieved<br>
                                ‚Ä¢ Activated automatically when loss exceeds ${bot.rotationState.wagerLossThreshold * 100}%<br>
                                ‚Ä¢ Returns to previous mode when balance recovers
                            </div>
